data.description: Well maintained 3 bedroom/2 bath conventional built ranch on a crawl space on a quiet cul-de-sac street. The property  entrance/driveway has a Private yard lined with cypress trees.  The home has an open concept with new flooring in the kitchen, dining room, living room and bathroom areas.  Beautiful crown molding in Living Room, butcher block counter tops and island with counter top seating . Bonus room off the kitchen with nook for a desk, futon or twin size bed and desk or dresser. The Nice 24 x 24 Detached Garage/Workshop with roll up doors, large enough for boat, mechanic shop, hobby shop. The extended concrete driveway provides lots of parking and an area to park a boat or RV.
